tar xzvf unix.tar.gz

Installation notes wer terribly hard to find; evenutally I found them at 
http://www.cs.arizona.edu/icon/docs/ipd243.htm

make X-Configure name=intel_linux
make Icon
make Samples
make Test
cd ~/bin/Linux-i686
ln -s ../src/icon-9.3.2/bin/icont .
